text.tspan: Think of some names for parts of the architecture

flowRoot.flowPara: Some secondary ECUs may not have enough flash for public key crypto, so the manifest may also be signed with a hmac for each ECU.
High Level Abstract transport between Primary and Secondary (PRO-3193)

The secondary needs to store metadata, but may lack a file system. Aktualizr should define the interface to the storage, with a concrete implementation that writes to a file on disk. For the embedded secondary, there will be a specific implementation in Octopoc
In-place JSON parsing for embedded ECU. Note that this component may get replaced with other serialization formats, e.g. ASN.1 DER/PER (PRO-3191)
